==Useful Info==
'''Thermic dynamos''' are fire-and-ice-themed [[nonliving]] monsters. They appear in the [[Elven Halls]] and in some [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
Their spells can bounce off walls, so you need to be careful about your position to avoid being [[multizap]]ped.

